# pyspark_db_utils  

It helps you with your DB deals
Will be updates soon.

Example of settings:0
```
settings = {
  "PG_PROPERTIES": {
    "user": "user",
    "password": "pass",
    "driver": "org.postgresql.Driver"
  },
  "PG_DRIVER_PATH": "jars/postgresql-42.1.4.jar",
  "PG_URL": "jdbc:postgresql://db.olabs.com/dbname",
}
```

